OL,3,CJanuary sales warning issued to
OL,4,Cbargain hunters by major bank
OL,6,FScammers may also offer heavily-
OL,7,Fdiscounted goods via social media.
OL,9,FClothing tends to be the most common
OL,10,Fitem purchased from the rogue
OL,11,Fretailers, followed by jewellery,
OL,12,FLloyds said.
OL,14,FLloyds said rogue retailer scams have
OL,15,Fcost #8.5 million between January and
OL,16,FNovember 2024, based on the group's
OL,17,Fown credit and debit card customer
OL,18,Fdata.
