OL,3,CJanuary sales warning issued to
OL,4,Cbargain hunters by major bank
OL,6,FThe bank has established an industry
OL,7,Fworking group, working with payments
OL,8,Fcompanies to protect shoppers by
OL,9,Freporting and blocking transactions
OL,10,Fwith known fake websites.
OL,12,FGavin Evans, senior manager for
OL,13,Fconsumer cards at Lloyds, said: "The
OL,14,FJanuary sales can be a good time to
OL,15,Fgrab bargains, but it's also a popular
OL,16,Ftime for rogue retailers, who try to
OL,17,Fscam unsuspecting shoppers and pocket
OL,18,Ftheir hard-earned cash.
