OL,3,CJanuary sales warning issued to
OL,4,Cbargain hunters by major bank
OL,6,F"To avoid being caught out, check the
OL,7,Fweb address before making a purchase
OL,8,Fto ensure that it is legitimate and
OL,9,Fmatches the shop you're looking to buy
OL,10,Ffrom, especially if you opened the
OL,11,Fwebsite by clicking on an advert or
OL,12,Fsocial media post.
OL,14,F"Remember that if something appears
OL,15,Ftoo good to be true, it usually is. If
OL,16,Fyou're ever unsure, consider buying
OL,17,Ffrom somewhere you trust instead."
OL,19,FHere are some tips from Mr Evans to
OL,20,Favoid losing money:
